      <title>公司会逐渐破产，而不是突然破产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2023-12-06/corporate-defaults-companies-are-going-broke-gradually-not-suddenly</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就像美国经济衰退或中国疫情后的反弹一样，预计今年将出现一波企业违约潮 —但没有发生。这并不意味着它不会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2023-12-06/corporate-defaults-companies-are-going-broke-gradually-not-suddenly</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 05:18:34 GMT</pubDate>
